  ],
  "remarks": "JSC MAK Vympel (a.k.a. Public Joint Stock Company Vympel Interstate Corporation) is a Russian military-industrial state enterprise that develops anti-ballistic missile systems and space control systems deployed by the Russian Armed Forces. Moreover, JSC MAK Vympel is part of the Almaz-Antey concern, a Russian state-owned arms manufacturer that develops anti-aircraft defence and cruise missile systems for the Russian military.",
